      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           #LVALI    BEGSR                           ** SR/#LVALI**
      *
      *   Reset work fields and indicators
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       ULVALI
     C                     MOVEA'0000'    *IN,31
     C*****                MOVEA'000'     *IN,50                          LLN021
     C                     MOVEA'00000000'*IN,50                          LLN021
     C                     MOVEA'00000'   *IN,58                          LLN021
