      *
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE 'BYM0053' ULMSID
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN52
     C                     EXSR #LSNMG
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ULVALI
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *                                                                   LLN021
     C           LLN021    IFEQ 'Y'                                       LLN021
      *                                                                   LLN021
      ** Validate Industry Code                                           LLN021
      **    Call industry code selection screen                           LLN021
     C           L#MIND    IFEQ '?  '                                     LLN021
