     C           L#MIND    IFNE *BLANKS                                   LLN021
     C                     MOVE L#MIND    L1MIND           Inst Code in BYLLN021
     C           L1MIND    CHAINBYINDRV0             90                   LLN021
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *ON                                       LLN021
     C                     MOVE 'BYM0073' ULMSID                          LLN021
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN59                           LLN021
     C                     EXSR #LSNMG                                    LLN021
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ULVALI                          LLN021
     C                     ENDIF                                          LLN021
      *                                                                   LLN021
     C                     ENDIF                                          LLN021
      *                                                                   LLN021
     C                     ENDIF                                          LLN021
      *                                                                   LLN021
     C           L#LINS    IFEQ *BLANKS                                   LLN021
     C           L#MIND    ANDNE*BLANKS                                   LLN021
     C                     MOVE 'BYM0154' ULMSID                          LLN021
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN52                           LLN021
     C                     EXSR #LSNMG                                    LLN021
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ULVALI                          LLN021
     C                     ENDIF                                          LLN021
      *                                                                   LLN021
     C                     ENDIF                                          LLN021
      *
      *   If screen details are valid then check whether records exists
      *   on BYACEXPP according to action code
     C           ULVALI    IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     MOVE L#ACOD    K1ACOD
     C                     MOVE L#LINS    K1LINS
     C           LLN021    IFEQ 'Y'                                       LLN021
     C                     MOVE L#MIND    K1MIND                          LLN021
     C                     ENDIF                                          LLN021
     C           KEY1      CHAINBYACEXPP            N90
      *
      *    If action is Insert record must not exist
     C           L#ACTN    IFEQ 'I'
     C           *IN90     ANDEQ*OFF
     C           L1RECI    ANDEQ'D'                                                           LLN022
     C                     MOVE 'BYM0075' ULMSID
     C                     EXSR #LSNMG
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ULVALI
