      **   If action is not Insert, Record must be live
     C           L#ACTN    IFNE 'I'
     C           *IN90     ANDEQ*OFF
     C           L1RECI    ANDNE'D'
     C                     MOVE 'BYM0086' ULMSID
     C                     EXSR #LSNMG
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ULVALI
     C                     ENDIF
